Guardly,is,a,mobile,personal,safety,application,that,lets,smartphone,users,push,a,single,button,on,their,device,to,connect,and,alert,friends,family,and,authorities,in,an,emergency,The,Guardly,API,gives,developers,the,ability,to,integrate,emergency,response,notification,and,collaboration,functionality,into,their,own,applications,Interested,developers,should,apply,with,the,provider,for,access,to,the,REStful,API,developer,key,and,documentation